      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is gone. the company, the house, all of it. the market just tanked and now i'm looking at millions in debt that i can't even begin to process. i just keep thinking about going back home and seeing the look on my parents' faces. i can't do it. the shame is just too much. there's literally no way to fix this.",
